00048 @synthesize request=request_;
00049 @synthesize status=status_;

00051 - (NSInteger) status {
00052         if(status_ == NSIntegerMax) {
00053                 if(self.error) {
00054                         if([self.error domain] == NSURLErrorDomain) {
00055                                 switch ([self.error code]) {
00056                                         case NSURLErrorUserCancelledAuthentication:
00057                                                 status_ = 401;
00058                                                 break;
00059                                         default:
00060                                                 break;
00061                                 }
00062                         }
00063                 } else {
00064                         status_ = [request_.URLResponse statusCode];
00065                 }
00066         }
00067         return status_;
00068 }
00069

00087 @dynamic success;

00089         return self.error == nil && [self wasSuccessful];
